      "acceptanceCriteria": "Governing equations and turbulence model selection are documented and justified; formal model form uncertainty quantification not required at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model was selected based on published literature for rotating blood pump flows. Formal model form uncertainty quantification is not required at MRL 2; justification is documented in the simulation report."
    },
