      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties and boundary condition inputs are documented with sources; formal sensitivity analysis not required at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Blood analog fluid properties sourced from FDA benchmark documentation. Boundary conditions derived from experimental measurements. Formal input uncertainty propagation is not required at MRL 2."
    },
